# ZAMBAHOLA plugin map

Install plugins from Cursor Marketplace (see `docs/ar/تثبيت-اضافات-السوق.md`). Full catalog: `docs/ar/المهارات-والروابط.md`.

## Required for this project

| Plugin | Use when |
|--------|----------|
| **zambahola-local** (repo MCP) | Read telemetry, Arabic analyst, queue remote commands |
| **zapier** | Slack/Sheets/GitHub alerts on directional hit |
| **tavily** | Market research, news, docs (replaces Perplexity for agent) |
| **huggingface-skills** | Papers, datasets, HF Jobs training, research import |
| **cli-for-agent** | Designing/fixing `npm run agent:*` scripts |

## Optional

| Plugin | Use when |
|--------|----------|
| **cursor-sdk** | Automate cloud agents from CI/scripts |
| **agent-compatibility** | Score repo agent-readiness |
| **continual-learning** | Auto-update AGENTS.md from sessions |

## Skill triggers (after install)

- Research / news → `tavily-search` or `tavily-research`
- HF papers/models → `hf-cli` / Hugging Face MCP tools
- Zapier setup → `zapier-setup` then enable GitHub · Sheets · Slack
- Local agent state → `zambahola_get_telemetry` / `zambahola_get_analyst`

## Safety

- No live Binance keys in repo; paper mode until directional ≥ 58%.
- Zapier writes (Slack/Sheets) need user confirmation before send.
